- "Median age of men surpasses 32 years" refers to a male median age greater than 32;
- "Median age of women is above the average median age of women in all states" refers to a female median age greater than the average female median age across all states.

- "giants with a population greater than half a million" refers to states with a total population greater than 500,000;
